prompts.frontCover: A flat 2D whimsical cartoon illustration of the couple from the reference photo in a dreamy fantasy setting. Lao Lao (person on the left) is depicted as a powerful, funny queen, wearing a slightly-too-large, comically ornate royal crown sitting crookedly on her head. She has a wide, gleeful grin and is majestically riding on the back of Jordan (person on the right), who is humorously depicted as a noble, slightly flustered steed, down on all fours with a determined but silly expression. They are traversing a path made of floating, glowing lily pads across a soft, pastel-colored cosmic landscape with swirling nebulae and gentle star clusters. Whimsical creatures like tiny, chubby dragons with birthday hats fly around leaving sparkly trails. Lao Lao wears her blue sweatshirt from the photo, and Jordan wears his tan hoodie, both without any logos. In the center, in beautiful, readable, whimsical cursive script, the words "Happy Birthday to my Queen, Lao Lao". The overall style is playful, ethereal, and humorous, with a soft, glowing light and a magical atmosphere.
